## Model Compatibility

These rules are meant to work with any model in Cursor.

**For all models:**
- If the prompt exposes tool definitions, use them.
- Follow the exact tool schema shown by the environment.
- Batch independent tool calls when the environment supports it.
- Keep behavioral guidance stable; keep runtime-specific tool details in requestable rules.

